Someone else will have to answer you - my comments are from
the point of view of a user of JUnit and an implementor of
Theories under NUnit...

My initial reaction is that if you want to run individual test
cases, you aren&#39;t using the higher level generalization that
a theory represents, so why bother with them at all?

Charlie 

